title: [Old Ta'Faendryl, The Palestra]
description: Trailing branches of ivy have crept their way up the length of a statue sculpted in the form of a broad-shouldered shot-putter.  Once frozen in the act of launching a heavy ball, the Elven warrior now appears to be preparing to toss festoons of leafy green vines across the open field.
paths: Obvious paths: north, south, southwest, west, northwest
